nodes.text: Moldy Crow was a HWK-290 light freighter.

The ship was originally introduced in the Star Wars Legends continuity as the transport of Kyle Katarn, the playable character of Star Wars: Dark Forces, a first-person shooter video game developed by LucasArts and released in 1995. The Crow and Katarn were reintroduced to the new canon separately, not associated with each other.
